Package: netops-server
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 18.0.0)
Maintainer: Tlink Technologies <support@tlink.io>
Description: NetOps Backend Server
 Optional standalone backend server for large-scale NetOps
 network device polling via SSH/SNMP. Offloads polling from
 the Electron desktop client to a centralized server.
 Supports REST API + WebSocket for real-time streaming.
 .
 Features:
  - SSH polling for 13+ network vendors
  - LLDP/CDP network discovery
  - Config backup and change management
  - WebSocket streaming for real-time updates
  - Connection pooling (50 max, 3 per host)
